# Trash Magic 

A universal philosophical language.  

We have the intention to build a world in a certain image, that of Trash Magic.  In this world we will build everything from trash, and build a culture which freely replicates everything we build.  

We express our intentions in sets of things.  These things are mapped to symbols.  Those symbols are turned into images, and traced into Geometron as Geometron Icon Glyphs.  These glyphs are then printed in physical media made from trash and manipulated in the physical world to communicate with other people for the replica